Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.96,0:01:54.01,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\t(0,400,\blur0.1)\t(400,401,\blur0)\t(5500,6050,\blur10)}毀此靈魂 只為救贖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.01,0:01:59.97,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\t(0,400,\blur0.1)\t(400,401,\blur0)\t(5500,5960,\blur10)}在生命終結之時 為內心帶來徹底甦醒
